OL,3,CWelsh Budget: #1.5billion extra for
OL,4,CWales but where's it being spent?
OL,6,FShe said: "Instead of taking this
OL,7,Fopportunity to steer Welsh families
OL,8,Faway from sky-rocketing childcare
OL,9,Fcosts, the Welsh Government has
OL,10,Finstead left them to fend for
OL,11,Fthemselves.
OL,13,F"Thousands of people from across Wales
OL,14,Fare being forced to make the difficult
OL,15,Fchoice between paying out of pocket
OL,16,Ffor childcare or leaving work.
