OL,3,CWelsh Budget: #1.5billion extra for
OL,4,CWales but where's it being spent?
OL,6,F"This shouldn't be the case, we want
OL,7,Fto see a universal offer of 30 hours
OL,8,Fof funded childcare per week for every
OL,9,Fsingle child in Wales between the ages
OL,10,Fof 9 months and 4 years old.
OL,12,F"By taking away the burden of
OL,13,Fchildcare costs, we can help people
OL,14,Fget back into work which will give our
OL,15,Feconomy a huge boost.
OL,17,F"The UK Labour Government have been
OL,18,Ftalking about encouraging more
OL,19,Feconomic growth, but it appears as
OL,20,Fthough their colleagues in Cardiff Bay
OL,21,Fdidn't get the message."
